   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "13.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "16.920", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass sich die Politik am Ende des Tages\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "16.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "18.000", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "am Ende des Tages, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "18.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "18.840", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "nicht vorher!\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "18.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "19.960", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "einmischt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "19.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "21.120", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "H\u00e4tten wir das nicht gemacht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "21.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "23.120", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "h\u00e4tten wir heute noch keinen Mindestlohn, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "23.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "27.600", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u00fcber den wir zum Beispiel morgen hier an dieser Stelle auch wieder sprechen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "27.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "29.800", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Kolleginnen und Kollegen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "29.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "33.400", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der Unternehmer Robert Bosch hat einmal gesagt:"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "33.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "36.160", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Immer habe ich nach dem Grundsatz gehandelt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "36.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "39.480", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "lieber Geld verlieren als Vertrauen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "39.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "42.040", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Unantastbarkeit meiner Versprechungen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "42.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "51.160", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der Glaube an den Wert meiner Ware und an mein Wort standen mir h\u00f6her als ein vor\u00fcbergehender Gewinn."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "51.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "51.600", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich glaube, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "51.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "54.600", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das ist der Kern dessen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "54.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "56.520", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was wir gerade im Moment diskutieren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "56.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "58.000", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es geht um Vertrauen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "58.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "62.560", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "gegenseitiges Vertrauen der Unternehmen in ihre Belegschaft, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "62.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "67.720", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber auch der Belegschaft in ihr Unternehmen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "67.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "71.480", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dieses Vertrauen wird immer h\u00e4ufiger ersch\u00fcttert. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "71.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "72.360", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn ein Unternehmen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "72.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "73.160", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie wir geh\u00f6rt haben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "73.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "74.560", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Milliardengewinne macht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "74.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "79.000", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber quasi im gleichen Atemzug ank\u00fcndigt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "79.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "80.320", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Stellen zu streichen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "80.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "82.240", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und zwar in merklichen Gr\u00f6\u00dfenordnungen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "82.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "84.360", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "zerbricht dieses Vertrauen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "84.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "86.920", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Und die Rekordgewinne, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "86.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "88.360", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die es verbuchen kann, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "88.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "91.120", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wurden von den Besch\u00e4ftigten erwirtschaftet, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "91.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "92.080", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "von den Menschen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "92.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "94.520", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die jeden Tag dort zur Arbeit gehen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "94.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "98.560", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber die m\u00fcssen jetzt vor Weihnachten um ihre Arbeitspl\u00e4tze f\u00fcrchten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "98.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "102.200", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist nicht nur schlimm und eine Katastrophe f\u00fcr die Besch\u00e4ftigten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "102.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "102.480", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nein, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "102.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "107.000", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das ist vielmehr auch eine Katastrophe f\u00fcr unseren ganzen Wirtschaftsstandort."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "107.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "112.480", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ein gro\u00dfes Unternehmen muss in der Lage sein, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "112.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "116.640", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "seine gut ausgebildeten und qualifizierten Kolleginnen und Kollegen\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "116.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "117.400", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ich bin \u00fcberzeugt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "117.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "118.680", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass es sie auch braucht\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "118.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "122.880", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
