   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "122.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "126.560", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "weiterzubilden und dann auch in neuen Branchen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "126.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "128.040", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die zukunftstr\u00e4chtig sind, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "128.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "129.200", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "einzusetzen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "129.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "134.600", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich habe es an dieser Stelle des \u00d6fteren gesagt und tue es jetzt auch noch einmal, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "134.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "136.880", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "weil es immer wieder wichtig ist. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "136.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "147.600", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Unternehmen wie auch die Besch\u00e4ftigten konnten sich immer auf ein sehr hohes Augenma\u00df ihrer Interessenvertretungen und insbesondere der Betriebsr\u00e4te verlassen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "147.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "152.000", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Betriebsr\u00e4te sind oftmals solche Mitarbeiter, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "152.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "155.720", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die schon l\u00e4nger in einem Unternehmen sind und ein Unternehmen besser kennen als mancher, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "155.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "156.840", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der kurzfristig die Geschicke lenkt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "156.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "160.280", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Diese haben uns auch durch die Finanzkrise gebracht. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "160.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "164.040", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Also vielen Dank an alle, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "164.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "168.160", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die als Betriebsr\u00e4tin oder Betriebsrat oder in den Gewerkschaften Verantwortung tragen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "168.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "174.480", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dies hat auch Gerhard Cromme, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "174.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "178.040", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der Aufsichtsratsvorsitzende von thyssenkrupp und von Siemens gewesen ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "178.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "178.760", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "noch einmal verdeutlicht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "178.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "181.040", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "als er 2012 sagte:"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "181.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "185.560", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Mitbestimmung in Deutschland hat in der Krise enorm geholfen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "185.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "189.920", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "189.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "192.880", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Rekordgewinne waren m\u00f6glich, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "192.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "195.040", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "weil die Menschen sich einsetzten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "195.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "200.160", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch deshalb ist der jetzt erfolgte Vertrauensbruch so problematisch. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "200.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "203.000", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Er ist ein falsches Signal an die restliche Belegschaft. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "203.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "205.480", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Er ist ein falsches Signal an die Jugend, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "205.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "206.480", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die nachkommt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "206.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "210.360", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die vielleicht in einem solchen Unternehmen arbeiten will. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "210.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "211.360", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich h\u00f6re immer wieder, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "211.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "216.960", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir Nachwuchsprobleme haben und Menschen brauchen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "216.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "218.200", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deshalb kann ich das nicht verstehen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "218.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "220.760", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich will auch dem Kollegen Bartsch recht geben: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "220.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "223.800", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
