   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "223.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "225.160", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deshalb ist es immer falsch, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "225.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "226.240", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "zu sagen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "226.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "227.960", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Trennt das!\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "227.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "228.720", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das kann man tun. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "228.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "231.760", 
   "id": "s000082", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dann muss man es aber konsequent tun. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "231.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "236.240", 
   "id": "s000083", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Man darf nicht auf der einen Seite nach dem Motto \u201eHaltet euch raus\u201c argumentieren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "236.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "241.520", 
   "id": "s000084", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "w\u00e4hrend man auf der anderen Seite bei allen Reisen des Wirtschaftsministers mitgenommen werden will, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "241.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "243.760", 
   "id": "s000085", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "F\u00f6rderungen bekommen m\u00f6chte usw."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "243.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "246.040", 
   "id": "s000086", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es darf also keine Einbahnstra\u00dfe sein. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "246.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "247.040", 
   "id": "s000087", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich w\u00fcrde mich freuen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "247.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "248.920", 
   "id": "s000088", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn man das \u00f6fters ber\u00fccksichtigte."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "248.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "250.440", 
   "id": "s000089", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u00dcber euren Gesetzentwurf, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "250.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "251.120", 
   "id": "s000090", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "liebe Linken, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "251.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "254.800", 
   "id": "s000091", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "k\u00f6nnen und werden wir in den Aussch\u00fcssen diskutieren und debattieren."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "254.800", 
   "children": [], 
